			<div class="content" id="post-content-4806438">
									

<p>I also thought this worked well without knowing the other material!</p>
<p>A couple of things I noticed:</p>
<blockquote>
<p>All pictures taken of the Coalition are immediately destroyed by localized data corruption on his face and identifying features.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>I feel like this was intended to either be something like &quot;All pictures taken of <em>the parathreat</em>&quot;; or &quot;All pictures taken <em>by</em> the Coalition&quot;.</p>
<blockquote>
<p>The box contained a large amount of confetti, classified documents from multiple Coalition member organizations, and the dismembered body of Agent Stormbreath.</p>
</blockquote>
<p>This was described as a small box; to me a small box is like, a jewelry box for example&#8230; so I got kinda confused picturing the dismembered body, and had to retrace a bit. That might just be me though.</p>
<p>Those are minor things of course—I had fun, I think it really pulled off the setting.</p>

