<p>First note &#8212; yep, that's a typo, it should have been &quot;by the Coalition&quot;.</p>
<p>Second note &#8212; small box in this context means about the size of an average Christmas present. (Note the date! Five days after the raid, which is on December 20th.) It *is* indeed to small to really fit a human body and that's intentional. Agent Stormbreath was really jammed in there.</p>

